Interface PopupWindowContext

All Superinterfaces:
java.io.Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
StandardPopupFilterWidget
public interface PopupWindowContext
extends java.io.Serializable

Interface for manipulating popup windows (each popup window corresponding to server-side "thread").

Author:
Taimo Peelo

Registers new thread-level service server-side and gives started service means of communicating with its opener and vice-versa.

Parameters:

properties - - properties specifying behaviour and appearance of creatable popup window.
